    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Drawing upon techniques to combat animated creatures, you bring a strike like an avalanche of stone.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Str 13, Stunning Fist.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>Before making a melee attack with an unarmed strike, you can expend one use of Stunning Fist to declare a stone-handed strike. Resolve the attack normally, except your attack ignores an amount of the target's hardness equal to your monk level or one-quarter your base attack bonus (minimum 1), whichever is higher. This effect replaces other effects or conditions that would be caused by your Stunning Fist.",
